me lembram piscinas.

204
00:10:00,733 --> 00:10:02,033
Oi, Snake.

205
00:10:02,067 --> 00:10:03,968
Sim. Ok,
Arthur.

206
00:10:12,044 --> 00:10:13,544
Lá está ela.

207
00:10:13,579 --> 00:10:15,480
Yick:
<i>Me sinto estranho.</i>

208
00:10:15,514 --> 00:10:16,714
Eu não me preocuparia.

209
00:10:16,748 --> 00:10:19,550
Essas coisas nunca
estiveram certas ainda.

210
00:10:19,584 --> 00:10:21,119
Estiveram sim!

211
00:10:21,153 --> 00:10:22,420
Oi, Melanie.

212
00:10:22,454 --> 00:10:24,255
Oi, Yick.

213
00:10:24,289 --> 00:10:28,159
Seus olhos são tão azuis,
eles parecem

214
00:10:28,193 --> 00:10:29,159
Piscinas.

