00:10:29,194 --> 00:10:30,161
Piscinas?

216
00:10:30,195 --> 00:10:32,729
O quê?!

217
00:10:35,501 --> 00:10:37,669
O que são piscinas?

218
00:10:37,703 --> 00:10:39,937
Piscinas?

219
