O que foi
tudo isso?

220
00:10:43,608 --> 00:10:45,276
Broomhead!

221
00:10:47,378 --> 00:10:49,279
Yick!

222
00:10:49,314 --> 00:10:50,915
Espere!

223
00:10:50,949 --> 00:10:52,249
Yick!

224
00:10:56,088 --> 00:10:59,557
Você tem que fazer
um teste de gravidez.

225
00:10:59,591 --> 00:11:01,058
